Comment: 0,0:24:11.11,0:24:11.94,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time:
Comment: 0,0:24:11.94,0:24:13.24,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A Day in the Platoon
Comment: 0,0:24:13.24,0:24:14.96,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Rio Runs!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.59,0:01:45.28,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,For now, you need to practice with the mouthpiece only.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.56,0:01:47.74,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Dissatisfied?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.90,0:01:49.55,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No! Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.10,0:01:55.38,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, I really want to play as well as Rio-senpai...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.03,0:01:57.76,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I am a Spartan, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.17,0:02:00.01,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, please teach me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.34,0:02:02.10,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Now it's time for breakfast.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.10,0:02:04.26,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The mess hall is over there. Go in first!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.26,0:02:05.42,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.84,0:02:16.17,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Knock, knock, sah, sah...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.19,0:02:22.98,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's work hard from today onwards.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.10,0:02:35.75,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.28,0:02:39.81,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Very Shitty!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.94,0:03:01.95,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs65\pos(640,112.5)}First Battle
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.94,0:03:01.95,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs65\pos(640,651.25)}The Story of the Chair
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.28,0:03:16.40,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, this was prepared for your arrival last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.40,0:03:18.57,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I tried my best to make it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.57,0:03:20.14,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.00,0:03:21.97,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Here, Rio.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.38,0:03:25.31,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you help me collect the dried seafood upstairs?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.31,0:03:28.21,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I don't know anything about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.21,0:03:29.49,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.49,0:03:33.68,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Try your best, Noël!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.68,0:03:35.86,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If you wanna sleep, please do it after you eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.21,0:03:38.82,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm trying my best. Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.12,0:03:43.42,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You are not at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.00,0:03:45.17,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm trying...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.75,0:03:51.44,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There... was Rio-senpai's...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.77,0:03:56.88,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Be quick. The meal is getting cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.66,0:04:10.69,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, let me introduce the personnel of the Platoon 1121 again.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.90,0:04:12.87,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's start with the platoon leader.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.00,0:04:19.37,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I am Felicia Heideman, Second Lieutenant. I'm the tank commander.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.66,0:04:21.28,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's have fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.74,0:04:23.78,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to meet you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.61,0:04:25.61,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.75,0:04:29.68,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, Noël.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.72,0:04:34.54,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Kannagi Noë...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.91,0:04:48.42,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She's Kannagi, Corporal. She's the driver.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.42,0:04:50.39,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Also, the mechanic.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.61,0:04:52.89,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to meet you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.86,0:04:57.52,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, the last one.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.01,0:05:03.62,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I am Suminoya Kureha, Private. I'm the gunner.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.03,0:05:12.16,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen. Though I am younger in terms of age, I am still a senior to you, so you must do as I say...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.38,0:05:19.14,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She probably ran out of strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.14,0:05:21.59,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for your hard work, Noël-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.10,0:05:27.93,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, shall we eat?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.93,0:05:28.71,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.66,0:05:30.64,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.87,0:05:34.49,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.87,0:05:38.47,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, let's eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.06,0:05:40.64,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.94,0:05:45.69,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.21,0:05:49.60,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I made this bacon by myself. Please eat a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.60,0:05:50.71,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.71,0:05:53.53,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Whether you do military missions or blow the horn, your body comes first.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.53,0:05:55.70,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Eat a lot and let your body grow!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.44,0:06:05.01,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I will try.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.06,0:06:10.78,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kureha.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.49,0:06:13.32,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.32,0:06:16.99,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,After breakfast, please take her for a walk around the base.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.55,0:06:22.52,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.98,0:06:27.78,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Attention!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.59,0:06:37.32,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, I'm busy and I don't want to do it at all, but since it's a command, I HAVE TO take you to walk around!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.32,0:06:38.52,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.52,0:06:40.87,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much, Kureha-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.87,0:06:43.78,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't address me as if you are a friend of mine, Private Sorami!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.78,0:06:44.81,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.81,0:06:48.31,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm. Private Suminoya-dono!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.54,0:06:53.08,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.08,0:06:55.56,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, first, let's salute the national flag and the platoon flag!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.54,0:06:57.35,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Salute!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.52,0:07:05.11,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Tank Platoon 1121 now has five soldiers.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.11,0:07:13.35,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Including one Second Lieutenant, one Sergeant Major, one Corporal and two Privates. Altogether five!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.35,0:07:15.76,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Private Suminoya-dono!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.27,0:07:19.83,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though this is the smallest formation, this is after all...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.60,0:07:24.71,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,An elite platoon!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.95,0:07:25.96,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, madam!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.75,0:07:34.08,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Our platoon is deployed with one tank, one heavy machine gun...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.08,0:07:39.11,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,...two light machine guns, four rifles and five handguns.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.96,0:07:46.79,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,With this war potential, we are ordered to protect the border around Seize and Trois!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.79,0:07:47.57,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.98,0:07:53.37,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Private S-Suminoya-dono, I have a question!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.66,0:07:59.58,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Good! You are permitted to speak! Private Sorami.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.89,0:08:05.83,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If I remem... If my memory is correct, isn't the other side of Seize...?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.48,0:08:09.75,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The other side of the mountain is indeed no man's land.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.55,0:08:17.10,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But our country, Helvetia, extends there anyway, so here is the border! The frontier!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.40,0:08:19.22,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It is an important strongpoint.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.45,0:08:24.04,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,For this reason, we take turns every night.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.04,0:08:25.86,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No absences allowed for two years!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.88,0:08:31.61,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the only hotline in the town that connects to other people.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.04,0:08:33.34,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.69,0:08:37.84,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,if it rings, we have to take it as the most important thing of all!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.84,0:08:42.78,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,In that situation, you need to wake up everybody, entering the first category of alarm condition immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.78,0:08:43.60,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.60,0:08:46.03,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Private Suminoya-dono!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.27,0:09:06.77,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The second floor contains the Captain's quarters and the briefing room.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.77,0:09:09.00,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Usually, trespassing is...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.40,0:09:11.72,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,free.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.51,0:09:14.28,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But you need to knock properly!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.66,0:09:16.26,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the bathroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.26,0:09:20.03,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Boiling the water for the bath is also a part of the cleaning duties!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.03,0:09:21.08,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And then...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.08,0:09:24.43,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The order of taking a bath also depends on ranking, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.76,0:09:30.54,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.71,0:09:34.68,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Because it is enjoyable to take baths together, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.68,0:09:37.22,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Platoon Leader! What are you doing!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.22,0:09:38.42,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I am cleaning the bathroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.42,0:09:40.70,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Noël is on duty today!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.70,0:09:42.78,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But she looked so tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.53,0:09:49.09,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,As the Platoon Leader, you're setting a bad example to the recruit by doing it yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.09,0:09:53.94,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I will do it later! A Platoon Leader needs to act as a Platoon Leader! Please get out of here immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.36,0:10:16.26,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, take a GOOD look at it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.59,0:10:24.69,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the main battle tank deployed to Platoon 1121, Vector 0 series self-walking tank, Takemicaduchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.69,0:10:27.02,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a lot bigger than the one on the training field!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.91,0:10:33.02,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the so-called tank of the zeroth generation!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.55,0:10:37.82,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,One of the only ten remainders from the old time in this country.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.82,0:10:41.46,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I've heard that they are really powerful tanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.61,0:10:44.44,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But, its feet...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.88,0:10:47.36,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It is being repaired.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.36,0:10:48.66,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't have enough parts.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.38,0:10:56.42,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,E-Even though the deployment manual is lost and we can't find the parts,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.42,0:11:00.42,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Noël will do something anyway, so no problem!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.05,0:11:03.40,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let you say it's a decoration!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.03,0:11:10.65,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This tank will stand, at some time, stand... for sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.00,0:11:15.94,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't take me for a fool.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.39,0:11:17.98,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's slow.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.25,0:11:22.18,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Our platoon is slow.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.18,0:11:25.85,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,People are calling us "The Burden Troop of Seize" or "Decoration."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.85,0:11:29.45,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We are the pink queens, but we don't even have a working tank.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.45,0:11:30.33,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But...!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.26,0:11:32.21,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kureha-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.58,0:11:35.59,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The walk around is over. Dismissed!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.68,0:11:40.47,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,They've become friends instantly, haven't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.99,0:11:42.09,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.46,0:11:45.60,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's exactly like when us two first met.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.95,0:11:48.07,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.05,0:11:51.68,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But I am a little bit bothered.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.68,0:11:55.10,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Last night, after you sent Kana-chan to bed...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.08,0:11:59.11,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Platoon Leader! Why is that girl a communicator!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.47,0:12:04.16,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you tell me that we were only recruiting for gun loaders and drivers?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.16,0:12:08.75,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to do this. It was Headquarters that sent the girl here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.75,0:12:11.21,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's usual that we don't get what we want.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.21,0:12:12.37,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But...!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.40,0:12:15.79,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,OK, OK. Everything is fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.79,0:12:17.09,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Rio will still love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.09,0:12:20.56,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Just like what we have now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.46,0:12:23.44,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course I am the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.07,0:12:31.86,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That girl is pretty perceptive. Maybe she's discovered something?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.72,0:12:33.92,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.36,0:12:37.27,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to do something.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.16,0:12:43.40,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It appeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.81,0:12:45.91,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.27,0:13:00.42,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A ghost?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.02,0:13:02.17,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.34,0:13:09.80,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's nonsense!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.80,0:13:12.86,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You must be half asleep, Noël!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.86,0:13:13.68,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,As expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.68,0:13:15.54,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean by saying "as expected!"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.54,0:13:17.44,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I also saw the ghost.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.56,0:13:20.44,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It was from the direction of our lodging, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.32,0:13:22.19,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.74,0:13:25.26,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you saying arbitrarily!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.94,0:13:28.19,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But generally speaking, ghosts exist, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.19,0:13:31.26,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I've said "STOP", OK?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.26,0:13:33.66,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Noël, you too?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.66,0:13:37.87,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,As a mechanic, you should completely investigate it in a scientific way before reporting it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.87,0:13:38.46,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.16,0:13:40.88,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.88,0:13:41.70,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.70,0:13:43.52,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about!?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.52,0:13:45.12,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way that ghosts exist!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.12,0:13:47.72,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No way! No way! Completely no way!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.18,0:13:58.14,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I have the same opinion as you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.55,0:13:59.51,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,For sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.51,0:14:01.52,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. There can't be ghosts.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.52,0:14:02.28,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No ghosts!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.28,0:14:03.35,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Definitely not!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.35,0:14:04.66,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Definitely definitely not!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.66,0:14:05.23,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.43,0:14:10.51,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Go and investigate carefully!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.51,0:14:13.39,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,In case of an emergency, sound your horn!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.39,0:14:15.44,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Reinforcements shall be sent immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.44,0:14:17.39,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why...?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.25,0:14:22.68,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me, Private-dono.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.68,0:14:25.83,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Kana... Private!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.83,0:14:27.51,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.82,0:14:29.23,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,kind of nervous!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.13,0:14:36.92,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The thunder is like an advancing march.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.92,0:14:39.75,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a mission, not a game!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.75,0:14:42.53,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, Kana...Private Sorami!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.53,0:14:44.92,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You go first. I will back you up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.92,0:14:45.77,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.77,0:14:47.10,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, penetrate!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.54,0:15:05.54,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The area around here is the same as it was before it was transformed into a fortress.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.04,0:15:08.55,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What was it before that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.55,0:15:11.11,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,How would I know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.11,0:15:12.66,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Just go now!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.66,0:15:13.55,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.31,0:15:42.16,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It is written in idea. What does it say?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.31,0:15:42.16,Sora Eng tl Note,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Idea is the fictional name they use for japanese in Sora no Woto.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.16,0:15:45.75,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't even read it, don't look at it any more.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.75,0:15:48.09,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It might be a beautiful story! If only I could read it...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.36,0:15:51.31,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't matter. It can only be some girl's nonsense.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.31,0:15:53.29,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Time for us to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.36,0:16:00.79,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not scared?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.79,0:16:01.60,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.20,0:16:04.37,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Clumsy...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.37,0:16:08.66,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Because ghosts are protecting us, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.66,0:16:09.78,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.78,0:16:15.88,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,In the village where I was born, we welcome ghosts every year, and we have a Thanksgiving festival for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.88,0:16:17.86,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Where the hell is that village.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.86,0:16:26.47,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ghosts possess people, suck their blood, make the corpse move, etc. They do a lot of bad things.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.54,0:16:41.69,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That was almost dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.69,0:16:46.02,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Rats spread bad diseases, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.47,0:16:48.56,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What? How come you're afraid too...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.42,0:17:00.61,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It looked as if...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.61,0:17:01.94,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It was there.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.34,0:17:12.08,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kureha? Private-dono?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.17,0:17:22.35,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess... Could it be that this place used to be a school?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.65,0:17:29.83,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Such a large school wouldn't exist, even in the capital.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.83,0:17:33.86,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But there must have been a lot more people before.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.86,0:17:41.61,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So in the past, the building must have been filled with kids our age studying together.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.56,0:17:43.45,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahh!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.45,0:17:45.46,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What? What? What!?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.46,0:17:48.19,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Music must have been taught here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.19,0:17:50.36,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't even a military place?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.23,0:17:52.56,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at this!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.24,0:17:56.42,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It won't change.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.66,0:18:00.84,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though I can't read the text...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.56,0:18:06.73,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,D sharp.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.32,0:18:09.90,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sound, won't change.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.55,0:18:32.41,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you daydreaming by yourself for?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.41,0:18:33.69,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What!?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.22,0:18:36.24,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kureha-chan! So beautiful!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.24,0:18:37.21,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What!?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.21,0:18:38.12,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.15,0:18:46.10,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The town of Seize, the fortress, and everybody in this platoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.79,0:18:55.54,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We are just a tiny platoon from the countryside that no one cares about.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.36,0:19:02.07,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The tank can't even move. Supply is almost forgotten.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.07,0:19:04.81,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, we barely look like a platoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.35,0:19:06.80,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We are about to disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.04,0:19:10.06,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But you like it very much, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.97,0:19:20.22,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What!? What!? What!?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.26,0:19:24.09,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's there!! It's there!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.09,0:19:25.80,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Kureha!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.64,0:19:31.53,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanata!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.40,0:19:44.56,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.56,0:19:46.12,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.49,0:19:54.42,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I am the gunner of the beautiful, {\i1}beautiful{\i0} and deeply-loved Platoon 1121!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.79,0:20:03.88,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You saw the true ghost?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.67,0:20:07.08,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there any way that this is a ghost?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.48,0:20:14.65,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you. You look a lot like the thief from yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.76,0:20:19.70,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This damn prat! I will eat you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.70,0:20:21.20,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't do that, Rio.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.20,0:20:23.31,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't threaten someone who's injured.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.31,0:20:24.36,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.73,0:20:28.74,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She doesn't have any other place to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.95,0:20:32.75,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And have you forgotten our platoon's coat of arms?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.04,0:20:37.50,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If you make her into a roasted bird, you are opposing your badge.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.02,0:20:39.98,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Shuko-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.98,0:20:41.59,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't even have to name her...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.43,0:20:44.72,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But I think she is beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.72,0:20:48.49,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't forget you almost died because of this prat yesterday!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.49,0:20:52.09,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But because of that, we had a big adventure today!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.68,0:20:54.52,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Kureha-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.72,0:20:56.56,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What are you talking about!?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.56,0:21:00.56,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't categorize that as an adventure!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.81,0:21:04.53,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Good grief. Let's decide by majority.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.85,0:21:07.98,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No. This is an order from the Platoon Leader.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.98,0:21:11.53,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If anybody eats her in secret, there will punishment, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.40,0:21:13.96,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Everybody got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.34,0:21:43.36,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.31,0:21:59.17,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It was Rio this morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.17,0:22:03.44,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If we let Kanata do it everyday, the people in town will complain.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.44,0:22:04.63,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.83,0:22:12.64,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kana-chan's seat is there.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.84,0:22:20.15,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kureha-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.84,0:22:24.62,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We found the same chairs by chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.62,0:22:27.48,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not custom made for you...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.48,0:22:28.90,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.65,0:22:32.52,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on! Release me!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.52,0:22:35.54,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you girls doing? That's dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.86,0:22:39.91,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Breakfast...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.96,0:24:14.96,Sora Eng Titles 1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs65\pos(640,268.75)}A Day in the Platoon - Rio Runs!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.11,0:24:14.96,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time: A Day in the Platoon - Rio Runs!
